messages.messageBody:
AAAAAGGGGHHHHH!!!! Virginia Beach?? You are in one of
my most favorite places I've ever visited! I went
there about 3 yrs ago with my sis who is a vendor at
different fairs and stuff (whose name is DeDe,
coincidentally)...and we did the Salem fair and fell
in love with Virginia and the kind people there.
Beautiful. Then we went to Virginia Beach...my two
older sisters, my niece, nephew, my son(2, then) and
my pregnant self...it was truly lovely. I was
seriously considering moving there for awhile. It's
still there in the back of my mind to, and sometimes
surfaces. :)
How are the homeschooling laws there?
Well, anyways, welcome to our list here, I know you'll
love it. I do. You can feel free to post anything with
this group.
-Bobbie
